text: Christina Forte (born 23 June 1967) is a Brazilian windsurfer. She competed in the 1992 Summer Olympics, the 1996 Summer Olympics, and the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian female sailors (sport) Category:Brazilian windsurfers Category:Sailors at the 1992 Summer Olympics – Lechner A-390 Category:Sailors at the 1996 Summer Olympics – Mistral One Design Category:Sailors at the 2000 Summer Olympics – Mistral One Design Category:Olympic sailors of Brazil
